# Auth State Flow - VitaGuard App

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[App Start] --> B[Supabase.initialize]
    B --> C[AuthGate Widget]
    C --> D{authControllerProvider}
    
    D -->|Loading| E[SplashScreen]
    D -->|Error| F[OnboardingScreen]
    D -->|Data = null| F
    D -->|Data != null| G{Route by Role}
    
    G -->|patient| H[MainPatient]
    G -->|doctor| I[MainDoctor]
    G -->|companion| J[MainCompanion]
    G -->|facility| K[MainFacility]
    
    C --> L[AuthController.build]
    L --> M[Subscribe to onAuthStateChange]
    L --> N[_init: load user data]
    
    M --> O{Auth Event}
    O -->|signedIn/tokenRefreshed| P[_loadUserData]
    O -->|signedOut/userDeleted| Q[state = null]
    O -->|error| R[state = error]
    
    P --> S[repository.getMe]
    S --> T[state = userData]
    
    U[Logout] --> V[repository.logout]
    V --> W[signOut scope: global]
    W --> X[state = null]
    X --> Y[ref.invalidateSelf]
    Y --> Z[All user-scoped providers invalidated]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style C fill:#d4edda
    style D fill:#fff3cd
    style O fill:#f8d7da
    style U fill:#f8d7da
```

## Key Components

### 1. AuthController (auth_provider.dart)
- **Type**: Riverpod `@riverpod` annotation with `keepAlive: true`
- **State**: `AsyncValue<Map<String, dynamic>?>`
- **Reactive**: Subscribes to `Supabase.instance.client.auth.onAuthStateChange`
- **Cleanup**: Cancels subscription on `ref.onDispose`
- **Logout**: Calls `signOut(scope: SignOutScope.global)` and invalidates self

### 2. AuthGate (auth_gate.dart)
- **Purpose**: App-level routing based on auth state
- **Loading**: Shows `SplashScreen`
- **Unauthenticated**: Shows `OnboardingScreen`
- **Authenticated**: Routes to role-specific main screen

### 3. SupabaseService (supabase_service.dart)
- **signOut()**: Uses `SignOutScope.global` to clear all sessions
- **invokeFunction()**: Logs `[FUNCTION]` tags for debugging
- **subscribeToPatientLiveVitals()**: Logs `[REALTIME]` tags and subscription status

## Critical Fixes Applied

1. **Reactive Auth State**: Replaced timer-based navigation with `onAuthStateChange` subscription
2. **Global SignOut**: `signOut(scope: SignOutScope.global)` prevents stale sessions
3. **Provider Invalidation**: `ref.invalidateSelf()` clears all user-scoped providers on logout
4. **Mounted Checks**: All async operations check `ref.mounted` before updating state
5. **Stream Cleanup**: `ref.onDispose` cancels `onAuthStateChange` subscription
6. **Structured Logging**: `[AUTH]`, `[STATE]`, `[ERROR]`, `[FUNCTION]`, `[REALTIME]` tags added

